RAMPATIOUS prompted the issue while racing three-wide and finished strongly. AFRICAN PRINCE saved ground while being allowed to settle in stride, came three-wide into the stretch but lacked a rally,. SUBITO SLEW was reserved off the early pace, came four-wide into the stretch and failed to threaten. MIQUEAS dropped back early and was not a factor.
